title: SUPER NAIL Professional Nail Liquid 4 oz
description: SuperNail Professional Liquids are made from Ethyl Methacrylate infused with UV inhibitors. Prevents nails from yellowing. Superior adhesive properties let you create acrylics that last.

title: EZ Flow A Polymer False Nails, Pink, 4 Ounce
description: It takes skill and a lot of training to create nails that define beauty and style. But durability is something that is not always in your control. That was until now. With our combination of Q Monomer and A Polymer powder. You will have it all. A Polymer Pink is blush pink in color and works great for pink and white nails. Working time is 35 45 seconds.

title: EZ Flow A Polymer False Nails, Clear, 4 Ounce
description: A Polymer and competition powders are the other part of the powerful equation for perfect nail enhancements. In seven classic, gotta have it colors, both work with our Q Monomer liquid.
